videos.description: Clint Capela gets the steal and slam, then a couple possessions later Trae Young goes up top to him for another dunk.

videos.description: Bogdan Bogdanovic gets JaVale McGee to bite on a pump fake, then puts in a floater right before the third-quarter buzzer.

videos.headline: Bogdanovic gets McGee to jump on third-quarter buzzer-beater

videos.description: Collin Sexton stares down his defender and drains the 3-pointer giving Cleveland the three-point lead with under 30 seconds remaining.
videos.headline: Sexton bottoms clutch 3

videos.description: Cleveland's Collin Sexton scores 27 points in a win over the Hawks, giving him six straight 20-point games to start the season. The last Cav to do so was LeBron James in 2004-05.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Sexton notches 6th straight 20-point game to start season; LeBron last to do so with Cavs ) 2021/01/02 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Sexton notches 6th straight 20-point game to start season; LeBron last to do so with Cavs
